verbose_text: Specifically, the infection of EC with R. rickettsii or R. conorii induces surface platelet adhesion; the release of von Willebrand factor from Weibel-Palade bodies; and increased expression of tissue factor, E-selectin, IL-1alpha, cell-adhesion molecules, and plasminogen activator inhibitor-1.
evidence: expression of tissue factor                                                           , E-selectin                            , IL-1alpha
